Link to "Other Services"
Other Services
Font Awesome use several other services to run
fontawesome.com
, the
content delivery networks
, communicate with users and customers,
      and operate its business:
Service
Privacy Notice
Description
Amazon Web Services
https://aws.amazon.com/privacy
Provides cloud servers and services for running websites.
