Protecting our legal rights and preventing misuse:
to protect the Services and our business operations; to prevent, detect and investigate fraud, misuse, harassment or other types of unlawful activities; where we believe necessary to investigate, prevent or take action regarding illegal activities, suspected fraud, situations involving potential threats to the safety or legal rights of any person or third party, or violations of this policy and our applicable agreements and terms of use.
-Identifiers
-Customer records
-Customer Support and Service information
-Commercial information
